title: 3DRPD
description: 3DRPD was established with the mission to provide the North American dental market with an outsourcing solution for the manufacturing of top-quality laser-sintered cobalt chrome partials. The company is headquartered in Montreal, Canada, and has operations in the United States, Europe, and Canada.
